# URL Canonicalization - Redirect all variations to primary URL
# For Cloudflare Pages

# Redirect www to non-www
https://www.heartsscan.org/* https://heartsscan.org/:splat 301

# Redirect trailing slashes (except root)
https://heartsscan.org/*/ https://heartsscan.org/:splat 301

# Redirect old domain to new domain
https://heart-scan.gta4372.workers.dev/* https://heartsscan.org/:splat 301
https://product-builder-pip.pages.dev/* https://heartsscan.org/:splat 301

# Handle SPA routing - serve index.html for all routes
/* /index.html 200
